    "body": "Possible workaround/implementation? (16:9 aspect ratio example)\r\n```js\r\n// 'win' as the BrowserWindow instance\r\nwin.on('resize', function () {\r\n  setTimeout(function () {\r\n    var size = win.getSize();\r\n    win.setSize(size[0], parseInt(size[0] * 9 / 16));\r\n  }, 0);\r\n});\r\n```"
